<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.283305>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1 – 6. Lutzomyia naiffi sp. nov. Holotype male. 1, Head frontal view, Bar: 200 µm. 2, Flagellomere II, Bar: 50 µm. 3, Wing, Bar: 500 µm. 4, Terminalia (a, style; b, coxite; c, paramere; d, lateral lobe; e, pump, genital filaments and aedeagus), Bar: 100 µm. 5, Style in ventral position. 6, Tip of genital filament." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/283305/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

